 This room (18m2) with lake view is suitable for singles or a couple. This boat is located near the Olympic Stadium. It has its own entrance which you directly enter from the jetty in front of the houseboat. The room has a very big sliding door window.

sleeping, bathing and living
 This room is modest in size but cleverly furnished and equipped with all comforts. The en-suite bathroom has a shower, sink, toilet and heating. Linen, towels and soap are provided. Next to a little cabinet with coffee and tea making facilities there is a small table to relax and to enjoy the river view. The room is furnished with a luxury kingsize bed.

key-less entry
 No Keys required at AMSTEL HouseBoat. Use your Phone and a digital key to open the door. Simple as that. We will send you an email with an App prior to your arrival. Just make sure Bluetooth is on and enter with the push of a button.

free bicycles
