Set in the most tranquil, green and charming neighborhood of Lido, Hotel Villa Orio e Beatrice is found in the Alberoni area, 1640 feet from the Circolo Golf Venezia. Rooms offer free wired internet.

Hotel Villa Orio e Beatrice offers an enchanting and exclusive view of the sun setting over the Venetian lagoon. The journey to Venice, by bus and water-bus, takes approximately 40 minutes.

Hotel Villa Orio e Beatrice is surrounded by a cool garden and features comfortable lounge areas. Rooms are tastefully furnished and feature air conditioning and a private bathroom with shower.

Breakfast includes cold meats and cheeses, cakes and pastries, yogurt and fresh fruit.

